{
  "texts": [
    "The reason for choosing RoBERTa is that it is the most recent model used in sentiment analysis with successful results in handling sarcasm.",
    "It has not just proved to be very successful in the task of sentiment analysis but to be successful with a variety of benchmark datasets, like social media posts, reviews, etc.",
    "The following subsections explain the steps proposed and conducted in this work to build the university recommendation system.",
    "Data preparationThe first step in using RoBERTa for sentiment analysis is to prepare the data.",
    "This involves selecting the dataset for training and testing the model, cleaning, and preprocessing the text data."
  ]
}